"when completion open enter selects highlighted item. 
inoremap <expr> <CR> pumvisible() ? "\<C-y>" : "\<C-g>u\<CR>"

"Took me a little while to get autocomplete to how I like it. 
"Is there a snippet? If so expand it. If not open 
"the autocomplete menu but DO NOT auto complete with the first entry.
"Only highlight the first selection
imap <expr><Tab> neocomplcache#sources#snippets_complete#expandable() ? 
            \ "\<Plug>(neocomplcache_snippets_expand)" 
            \ : pumvisible() ? "\<C-n>" 
            \ : "\<C-x>\<C-u>\<C-p>\<lt>Down>" 


